channel.title: Do not understand
channel.description:
For some reason, when I try to load the MoparScape web client, it wont let me. It comes up with some page that says "Error Loading RuneScape."
Also, when I try to log into a server that is up 100% of the time, it won't let me, it says it is down.
I need to know how to log into a server that includes other players, and also where I can post a topic where I can talk about my ideas for a Machima, (sort of like Red Vs Blue), and ask for other, more experienced programmer's help in the matter.
